enum SRM::SRM_Coordinate_Valid_Region_Code
 

Enumeration values:

COORDVALRGN_EXTENDED_VALID  EXTENDED_VALID denotes a coordinate that is contained in the extended valid region and in the CS domain but not in the valid region.

enum SRM::SRM_CS_Code
 

Enumeration values:
CSCOD_UNSPECIFIED  Unspecified.
CSCOD_EUCLIDEAN_3D  Euclidean 3D.
CSCOD_LOCOCENT_EUCLIDEAN_3D  Localized Euclidean 3D.
CSCOD_EQUATORIAL_SPHERICAL  Equatorial Spherical.
CSCOD_LOCOCENT_EQUATORIAL_SPHERICAL  Localized spherical.
CSCOD_AZIMUTHAL_SPHERICAL  Azimuthal spherical.
CSCOD_LOCOCENT_AZIMUTHAL_SPHERICAL  Localized azimuthal spherical.
CSCOD_GEODETIC  Geodetic 3D.
CSCOD_PLANETODETIC  Planetodetic 3D.

Geodetic 3D with longitude in opposite direction.

CSCOD_CYLINDRICAL  Cylindrical.
CSCOD_LOCOCENTRIC_CYLINDRICAL  Localized cylindrical.
CSCOD_MERCATOR  Mercator and augmented Mercator map projection coordinate systems.
CSCOD_OBLIQUE_MERCATOR_SPHERICAL  Oblique Mercator and augmented oblique Mercator map projections of a sphere.
CSCOD_TRANSVERSE_MERCATOR  Transverse Mercator and augmented transverse Mercator map projections.
CSCOD_LAMBERT_CONFORMAL_CONIC  Lambert conformal conic and augmented Lambert conformal conic map projections.
CSCOD_POLAR_STEREOGRAPHIC  Polar stereographic and augmented polar stereographic map projections.
CSCOD_EQUIDISTANT_CYLINDRICAL  Equidistant cylindrical and augmented equidistant cylindrical map projections.
CSCOD_SURFACE_GEODETIC  Surface geodetic.
CSCOD_SURFACE_PLANETODETIC  Surface planetodetic.

Surface geodetic with longitude in opposite direction.

CSCOD_LOCOCENTRIC_SURFACE_EUCLIDEAN  Localization of Euclidean 2D CS into plane surface in 3D position-space.
CSCOD_LOCOCENTRIC_SURFACE_AZIMUTHAL  Localization of azimuthal CS into plane surface in 3D position-space.
CSCOD_LOCOCENTRIC_SURFACE_POLAR  Localization of polar CS into plane surface in 3D position-space.
CSCOD_EUCLIDEAN_2D  Euclidean 2D.
CSCOD_LOCOCENT_EUCLIDEAN_2D  Localized Euclidean 2D.
CSCOD_AZIMUTHAL  Azimuthal coordinate system.
CSCOD_LOCOCENT_AZIMUTHAL  Localization of azimuthal CS.
CSCOD_POLAR  Polar coordinate system.
CSCOD_LOCOCENTRIC_POLAR  Localized polar.
_enumInt  Local Space Polar 2D SRFT.
_INVALID_INPUT

the SRM_Axis_Direction object from its enumerant value
